# Capability-ask for the uppercase reference extension.
#
# Embedded into example_uppercase_extension.wasm's
# `stardog.capability-ask` custom section by `wf-embed-ask embed`
# to produce example_uppercase_extension_with_ask.wasm. Used by
# CapabilityAskIT to prove the auto-insertion + overwrite-on-
# reload flows end-to-end.
#
# The uppercase extension imports no host callbacks; the ask
# lists http-callbacks and a rationale so the SPARQL round-trip
# has real triples to fetch back.

@prefix cap: <http://semantalytics.com/2021/03/ns/stardog/webfunction/capability#> .

<> a cap:CapabilityAsk ;
    cap:asksInterface cap:HttpCallbacks ;
    cap:asksHost "api.example.com" ;
    cap:asksRationale "Integration-test ask for uppercase extension: no callbacks required, HTTP host declared for cross-axis coverage." .
